# ─── Rust ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
target/
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb

# Cargo lock — keep for binaries, ignore for libraries
# This is a binary crate, so Cargo.lock is intentionally tracked.
# Remove the next line if you want to commit Cargo.lock.
# Cargo.lock

# ─── Environment & Secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ─── SQLx offline query cache ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
